{{Notability|Institutions|date=April 2016}}

'''ASUE''' (''Arbeitsgemeinschaft für Sparsamen und Umweltfreundlichen Energieverbrauch e. V.'') -  The Association for the Efficient and Environmentally Friendly Use of Energy - is a [[Germany|German]] association founded in 1977. 

The association's aim is to assist in the development and production of energy-saving and [[eco-friendly]] technologies. Its members include over 40 companies and [[corporation]]s in the German gas industry.

