{{about|the book|the film by the same title|We Bought a Zoo}}
{{refimprove|date=June 2012}}{{italic title}}
'''''We Bought a Zoo''''' is a book published in 2008 by Benjamin Mee about his experiences in purchasing the Dartmoor Wildlife Park in [[Devon]], England in 2006. Renamed the [[Dartmoor Zoological Park]], it was reopened to the public the following year.

The book was loosely adapted into a [[We Bought a Zoo|film of the same name]] that was released in 2011.

The book was published by [[Harper Collins]] ({{ISBN|978-0007274864}}).<ref>{{cite web|title=We Bought a Zoo|url=http://www.harpercollins.co.uk/Titles/40949/we-bought-a-zoo-benjamin-mee-9780007274888|work=Harper Collins|accessdate=2 June 2012}}</ref>

